ABOUT US



North Florida Sales
North Florida Sales is a locally owned and operated company.  Started in 1995, NFS strives to be a leader in sales and service in the beverage industry in Jacksonville and Lake City, FL.  Our owner and President, Pinky Pelham, has over 40 years in the beer industry, having owned and operated distributorships in Kentucky as well as Florida.  North Florida Sales distributes Anheuser-Busch products as well as fine import and craft brands along with non-alcoholic brands and spirits.
Territory
North Florida Sales covers all or part of 11 counties in Florida.  These counties include:



Duval
Nassau
St. John's
Putnam
Clay
Bradford




Union
Baker
Columbia
Hamilton
Suwannee











Mission
To provide the highest quality customer service on a cosistent basis, while ensuring the availability of the freshest and cleanest product possible.
Vision
To be regarded as a model of professionalism and efficiency in the wholesale distribution industry.
Values
To maintain a professional relationship among peers and retail customers.  To maintain a clean professional image reflected through attitudes and condition of equipment.



